---
// Figure: Minimal verification receipt
// Five-step sequence. Holder-visible receipt, with a short "Not created" note below.
---

<div class="reveal my-12 md:my-16">
  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border overflow-hidden" style="background: rgba(11,11,17,0.6);">
    <div class="p-6 md:p-8">

      <div class="mb-6">
        <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-1">Verification event</p>
        <h3 class="text-text-primary font-display font-bold text-lg tracking-tight">Minimal verification receipt</h3>
      </div>

      <ol class="space-y-0 divide-y divide-border/40">
        <li class="grid grid-cols-[2rem,1fr] gap-4 py-3 items-start">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-text-tertiary pt-1">01</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm font-display font-semibold">Present credential</p>
            <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs leading-relaxed">holder → checker</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="grid grid-cols-[2rem,1fr] gap-4 py-3 items-start">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-text-tertiary pt-1">02</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm font-display font-semibold">Request minimum claims</p>
            <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs leading-relaxed">checker asks only what the use case requires</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="grid grid-cols-[2rem,1fr] gap-4 py-3 items-start">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-text-tertiary pt-1">03</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm font-display font-semibold">Approve disclosure</p>
            <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs leading-relaxed">holder consents on the holder service</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="grid grid-cols-[2rem,1fr] gap-4 py-3 items-start">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-text-tertiary pt-1">04</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm font-display font-semibold">Verify</p>
            <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs leading-relaxed">checker confirms status and integrity against the issuer</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="grid grid-cols-[2rem,1fr] gap-4 py-3 items-start">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-text-tertiary pt-1">05</span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm font-display font-semibold">Emit holder-visible receipt</p>
            <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs leading-relaxed">checker · purpose · claims disclosed · result · time · retention</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <!-- Not created note -->
      <div class="mt-6 pt-5 border-t border-border/50">
        <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-3" style="color: rgba(239,68,68,0.75);">Not created by this event</p>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-xs text-text-secondary">
          <li class="grid grid-cols-[0.9rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
            <span class="font-mono text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: rgba(239,68,68,0.6);">−</span>
            <span>No universal behaviour log</span>
          </li>
          <li class="grid grid-cols-[0.9rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
            <span class="font-mono text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: rgba(239,68,68,0.6);">−</span>
            <span>No unnecessary cross service trace</span>
          </li>
          <li class="grid grid-cols-[0.9rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
            <span class="font-mono text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: rgba(239,68,68,0.6);">−</span>
            <span>No open ended retention</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs mt-3 text-center italic">
    A check that can be reviewed later requires a minimal receipt, not just a pass or fail result.
  </p>
</div>
